`FirstOrder.Language.IsExtensionPair_iff_exists_embedding_closure_singleton_sup` is a characterization of `FirstOrder.Language.IsExtensionPair` in terms of extending the domain of an embedding.
`FirstOrder.Language.isFraisseLimit_of_countable_nonempty_dlo` shows that any countable nonempty
  model of the theory of linear orders is a Fra√Øss√© limit of the class of finite models of the
  theory of linear orders.
`FirstOrder.Language.isFraisse_finite_linear_order` shows that the class of finite models of the
  theory of linear orders is Fra√Øss√©.
